skins.shipDescription: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm the CPU of Lowee, White Heart. I have two little sisters. Although they are mischievous prankers and a handful to look after, they're still very cute. Next time, why don't we all play together?
skins.acquisition: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
skins.login: So damn slow... Ugh. How long are you gonna keep me waiting?
skins.secretaryIdle1: How long do I have to keep waiting here? My tech is gonna go obsolete at this rate.
skins.secretaryIdle2: Am I angry? ... It's just how I talk, don't worry about it.

skins.shipDescription: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...
